                  OAC DC MACRO

PURPOSE: TO PROVIDE A CONVIENIENT METHOD OF GENERATING
          PARAMETER LISTS WITHIN A MACRO FOR MF=L PROCESSING

SYNTAX:
LBL     OACDC ARG,TYPE=A,DEF=0,COM=

LBL     A LABEL TO BE GENERATED ON THE DC

ARG     THE ARGUMENT WHICH IS TO APPEAR WITHIN THE SCOPE OF THE DC
           IF THIS IS NULL, THE VALUE CODED AS DEF= WILL BE
           SUBSTITUTED.

TYPE=   THE TYPE OF DC DEFAULTS TO A. EXAMPLES: TYPE=AL2 , TYPE=F

DEF=    THE DEFAULT VALUE TO BE SUBSTITUTED IF ARG IS NULL

COM=    A COMMENT TO BE PUT ON THE GENERATED STATEMENT
